{"remainingRequest":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js??ref--1-1!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js??ref--1-2!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/operable/enough-time/content-change-can-be-stopped.md?vue&type=template&id=adaa827e&","dependencies":[{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/operable/enough-time/content-change-can-be-stopped.md","mtime":1540958169739},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/loaders/templateLoader.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js","mtime":1533872387000}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":["\n<div class=\"content\"><h1 id=\"持续的内容变化可停止\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#持续的内容变化可停止\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 持续的内容变化可停止</h1>\n<h2 id=\"描述\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#描述\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 描述</h2>\n<p>对于移动、闪烁或者滚动等行为会带来持续的内容变化，对于有认知障碍的用户在内容变化的时间之内可能获取不到所需要的信息，需要提供一种机制来暂停或者停止这种内容变化。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例子\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#例子\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 例子</h2>\n<h3 id=\"good-case\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#good-case\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> good case</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>一个播放滚动新闻的页面提供一个功能按钮暂停滚动，再次点击按钮恢复滚动</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"指导建议\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#指导建议\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 指导建议</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>对于自动启动或者持续时间超过5秒以上的任何移动，闪烁或滚动信息，提供一种机制供用户暂停，停止或隐藏它。除非移动、闪烁或滚动是必须的。</li>\n<li>对于自动更新，提供一种机制供用户关闭它，除非自动更新是必须的。</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",null]}